favourite.article:
Once it was my working,
 His it hence shall be;
Once I tried to use Him,
 Now He uses me;
Once the pow’r I wanted,
 Now the Mighty One;
Once for self I labored,
 Now for Him alone.

O Lord Jesus! this hymn really exposed me! Lord continually shatter me! O continue to break my soulish humanity and continue to dispense more of Your divine nature to my Spirit! O use me Lord! Make Your will also my will! I just want You Lord! O I love You Lord Jesus!
